Ya, sayang.

00:11:33.120 --> 00:11:34.040
J.

00:11:34.480 --> 00:11:37.680
Kami akhirnya menjadi
saudara dari mitra bisnis.

00:11:37.880 --> 00:11:40.400
Selamat!
